hnung.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 7aHISTORY / Ancient / General.2bisacsh1 aFink, Gerhard, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHerrmann, Gerd.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Philosophy 2000 - 2014z9783110636949oZDB-23-GPH08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET TUSCULUM ONLINEz9783110363272oZDB-23-DTO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV/AV  Altertum 2005-2012z9783110345643oZDB-23-OAT0 cprintz978305005455140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978305009189140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783050091891423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783050091891.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DTO  aZDB-23-GPHc2000d2014  aZDB-23-OATc2005d2012